Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村长…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜？
